message.body: We are back at the house now with pie face and Jamie
Hi ya Kate, the group wanted to know how things were going at the bootleg?Are you still there? We're going to jump in a cab soon to get home x x
Ok, I'm back home now so if you guys don't mind cabbing it back it'll save me turning out again :) hope Marty and elayne rocked your worlds. See you to take you to a brekkie spot in the morning!
Sounds great, we are heading your way in a bit!
I'm parked on park - see you soon?!

Kate, big thanks/ you're awesome to you and tommy for making this such a fun trip and giving some old (and new) pals a great time together. Thanks for giving up your living room for a week to a scruffy fella from the other side of the country. You and tommy were the most hospitable and were wonderful ambassadors to LA. Hope our paths cross again and of course, best of luck with little Pearl! Much love, ######
